msgid ""
"{ref}`reading-nix-language` to learn about the Nix language, which is used "
"to declare packages and configurations."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/first-steps/reproducible-scripts.md:101
msgid ""
"{ref}`declarative-reproducible-envs` to create reproducible shell "
"environments with a declarative configuration file."
msgstr ""

